OL,6,FA man was caught smiling on CCTV
OL,7,Fmoments after stabbing his wife to
OL,8,Fdeath and leaving their baby behind in
OL,9,FBradford, a jury has been told.
OL,11,FKulsuma Akter suffered more than 25
OL,12,Fknife injuries in an attack by Habibur
OL,13,FMasum after he confronted her in the
OL,14,Fstreet while she was pushing their
OL,15,Fseven-month-old son in a pram on April
OL,16,F6 last year.
