OL,3,CMurder accused 'was seen grinning on
OL,4,Cbus CCTV after stabbing wife to death'
OL,6,FA trial has heard that Masum, aged 26,
OL,7,Ftracked Ms Akter, aged 27, to a refuge
OL,8,Fin Bradford, where she had been
OL,9,Fstaying after he allegedly held a
OL,10,Fknife to her throat following an
OL,11,Fassault at their home in Oldham in
OL,12,FNovember 2023.
OL,14,FGiving his closing speech to jurors on
OL,15,FTuesday 24 June, prosecutor Stephen
OL,16,FWood KC showed jurors CCTV of Masum
OL,17,Fwalking through Bradford after the
OL,18,Fattack, saying there were no signs of
OL,19,Fhim being "distressed", as he had
OL,20,Fclaimed in his evidence.
