OL,3,CMurder accused 'was seen grinning on
OL,4,Cbus CCTV after stabbing wife to death'
OL,6,FMr Wood told Bradford Crown Court that
OL,7,Fa close-up of Masum getting on a bus
OL,8,Fshowed him smiling, which "removed all
OL,9,Fpossible doubt" about his state of
OL,10,Fmind.
OL,12,F"There were no tears, there was no
OL,13,Fdistress. Perhaps, members of the
OL,14,Fjury, the smile you can clearly see
OL,15,Fform as he gets on that bus is as a
OL,16,Fresult of him thinking at that point
OL,17,Fhe's getting away. The smiling killer."
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@OO]tD@AOUyD@gO]
