OL,6,FMr Wood said that although Masum was
OL,7,Fsuffering from depression at the time,
OL,8,Fthat did not provide an explanation
OL,9,Ffor the killing.
OL,11,F"It was not his depression which
OL,12,Fcaused him to kill Kulsuma, it was his
OL,13,Fother longstanding personality traits
OL,14,Fof controlling behaviour, jealousy and
OL,15,Fparanoia. She had rejected him. She
OL,16,Fhad to die," he said.
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
