OL,3,CMurder accused 'was seen grinning on
OL,4,Cbus CCTV after stabbing wife to death'
OL,6,F"And were there any residual thought
OL,7,Fthat this was about seeing his son `
OL,8,Fhaving left his wife literally in the
OL,9,Fgutter, bleeding to death, he leaves
OL,10,Fhis son alone.
OL,12,F"He could so easily have walked away
OL,13,Fwith him. But he knew if he walked
OL,14,Faway with that pram it would increase
OL,15,Fhis chances of getting caught.
OL,17,F"But he very quickly got himself out
OL,18,Fof the area and down to Aylesbury.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
