OL,3,CMurder accused 'was seen grinning on
OL,4,Cbus CCTV after stabbing wife to death'
OL,6,F"In the meantime he changed his
OL,7,Fappearance ` shaved his beard, cut his
OL,8,Fhair, changed his clothing."
OL,10,FMr Wood said the relationship between
OL,11,FMasum and Ms Akter was "an abusive
OL,12,Frelationship characterised by his
OL,13,Fjealousy, possessiveness and
OL,14,Fcontrolling behaviour with violence
OL,15,Fbeing both used and threatened".
OL,17,FMr Wood told jurors that in July 2023
OL,18,FMs Akter went to stay with her brother
OL,19,Fbecause of Masum's controlling
OL,20,Fbehaviour, leading him to threaten to
OL,21,Fharm himself with a knife.
