OL,4,Cbus CCTV after stabbing wife to death'
OL,6,FThe prosecutor said that over two days
OL,7,Fin November 2023, Masum "abused his
OL,8,Fwife" by assaulting her, threatening
OL,9,Fto kill her and holding a knife to her
OL,10,Fthroat when she received an innocuous
OL,11,Fmessage from a male colleague at the
OL,12,Fcake factory where she worked.
OL,14,F"That was his jealousy. Once more, he
OL,15,Ftook possession of a knife. The next
OL,16,Ftime it would have fatal
OL,17,Fconsequences," Mr Wood said.
OL,19,F"He is a man who resorts to
OL,20,Fviolence... and when he resorts to
OL,21,Factual violence, it's with a knife."
