OL,6,FMasum said during the trial that he
OL,7,Fhad taken a knife with him on the day
OL,8,Fhe killed Ms Akter because he intended
OL,9,Fto stab himself if she did not "listen
OL,10,Fto him".
OL,12,FMr Wood said Masum's threats of self-
OL,13,Fharm were "empty threats", adding: "He
OL,14,Fhas never made an attempt on his own
OL,15,Flife, he has never harmed himself.
OL,16,FThese are examples of his emotional
OL,17,Fblackmail."
