OL,6,FHe told jurors that during the fatal
OL,7,Fattack on Ms Akter, Masum put her on
OL,8,Fthe ground, stabbed her "many, many"
OL,9,Ftimes, kicked her "as a final insult",
OL,10,Fthen took hold of the back of her head
OL,11,Fand cut her throat.
OL,13,FMr Wood said: "Such a brutal and
OL,14,Fviolent assault by the defendant,
OL,15,Fculminating in a deliberate cutting of
OL,16,Fhis wife's throat, only points to an
OL,17,Fintention to kill. That is what he
OL,18,Fwanted, that is what he did."
