OL,6,FMasum denies murdering Ms Akter but
OL,7,Fhas pleaded guilty to manslaughter and
OL,8,Fpossession of a knife.
OL,10,FHe also denies two charges of assault,
OL,11,Fone count of making threats to kill
OL,12,Fand one charge of stalking.
OL,14,FThe trial continues.
